just_use config.go

# label: SIMPLE
# role: supports feature — JSON config loader (mode/root/port)

Two modes: "prod" (durable) vs "demo" (auto-nuke via GOPHER_RESET_DB=1).
root must be creatable; gopher.db and uploads/ live under it. No env-var
overrides — the whole config comes from one JSON file pointed at by
GOPHER_CONFIG, which keeps deployment boringly explicit.
